{"tid":2219492,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"解放軍「環保式」靠嚇 導彈片段被揭用舊貨","createTime":"2020-09-27T02:04:53.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-27T03:55:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"55dd732c0c6fdd0bd94d0b1661cbb58a5271726a","tid":2219492,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:04:53.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200927/FEDBCB5E45GVJLYDMADNI7KZQ4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200927%2FFEDBCB5E45GVJLYDMADNI7KZQ4%2F&d=31jm0GaxjznMjcF0xOQh0ktrSvVb5AcF94AlmVXjqEc%3D&h=36b8840c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20200927%2FFEDBCB5E45GVJLYDMADNI7KZQ4%2F&h=79833487\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20200927/FEDBCB5E45GVJLYDMADNI7KZQ4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n解放軍「環保式」靠嚇 導彈片段被揭用舊貨<br />\n<br />\n《解放軍報》前日發佈的東部戰區「東風-11導彈十連發」影片，。。。。。。。。。。，如今再增一宗醜聞。<br />\n<br />\n十連發影片於前日由《解放軍報》發佈，但未說明時間、地點及發射飛彈型號。中共喉舌《環球時報》等多家媒體紛紛轉發，聲稱片中導彈為「東風-11A導彈」。鑑於東部戰區專責對台作戰，東風-11系列的導彈被視為對台主要武器，該影片的恫嚇意味濃厚。台蘋後來發現十連發影片與央視2016年12月的「2016火箭軍大演兵」影片完全相同，連爆破物飛射角度也一模一樣；十連發影片一開始為解放軍部隊從山區基地出發，但下個鏡頭便變成去到戈壁沙漠，剪接的斧鑿痕迹更是明顯。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/i5E4nKYmAHnTqZD5FS-14-3Rc9M=/1125x874/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/TRYMIL3525CLFBEMN7VZC6SFA4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fi5E4nKYmAHnTqZD5FS-14-3Rc9M%3D%2F1125x874%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FTRYMIL3525CLFBEMN7VZC6SFA4.jpg&h=61b93ecd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n炸關島挪用電影片段<br />\n<br />\n解放軍上周才弄虛作假，其空軍發佈的模擬轟炸關島畫面，竟是來自《變形金剛2》等荷李活電影。美國安德森空軍基地指揮官斯隆直言：「這影片本身純粹只是宣傳，目的在脅迫我們和製造敵意」。<br />\n<br />\n台灣蘋果新聞網"},{"pid":"a99137949eff1d7a52a3702e10e2540ad965b8cd","tid":2219492,"uid":74361,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:05:57.000Z","msg":"天能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d9e4c4467031c7c17886d06247436171f67418f","tid":2219492,"uid":121146,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:10:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到底e個垃圾廢國有幾窮  一支都冇錢射"},{"pid":"81c7285474d5fa6cefe459c00aa4d7ed6fcdb182","tid":2219492,"uid":41298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a99137949eff1d7a52a3702e10e2540ad965b8cd","tid":2219492,"uid":74361,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:05:57.000Z","msg":"天能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:10:53.000Z","msg":"逆向導彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80752181110403b1e31061c822544b9877fe739b","tid":2219492,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"81c7285474d5fa6cefe459c00aa4d7ed6fcdb182","tid":2219492,"uid":41298,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a99137949eff1d7a52a3702e10e2540ad965b8cd","tid":2219492,"uid":74361,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:05:57.000Z","msg":"天能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:10:53.000Z","msg":"逆向導彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:13:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a494176aafab21da442294da128472e860303c9","tid":2219492,"uid":228868,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-27T02:14:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"